column1: Admin can not modify date in Date Added field if it is not filled previously
column26:
Admin can not modify date in Date Added field if it is not filled previously



Steps to Reproduce

#  Go to Retail website>Catalog>Reviews
#  Click on Edit Review button
#  Click on Date Added calendar icon 
#  Modify previous Date Added field 



Expected Result

Admin should be able to select another date to modify Date Added field



Actual Result

Admin is not able to select another date to modify Date Added field
